{"id": 1560, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X兰蔻】你在“折腾你的脸”这件事上都走过什么弯路？", "description": "过于懒惰，疏于防晒，过度清洁，脸太干……简直走过了一整个盘山公路啊。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6955, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170313122739ogTXqAuZDlBPF4jt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-13T03:00:21Z", "options": [{"id": 178435, "content": "越控油越油\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852189}, {"id": 180483, "content": "抹了这么多年也不知道什么适合自己？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974078}, {"id": 178436, "content": "迷信国外化妆品、护肤品", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933594}, {"id": 178438, "content": "相信纯植物这种愚蠢的说法", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946232}, {"id": 179462, "content": "关于肤色，什么一黄二白的是什么意思？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 861525}, {"id": 178439, "content": "看到大家这样我就放心了 一直以为只有我是这样 看美妆视频的博主皮肤好的不真实 虽然也有好的啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619263}, {"id": 178440, "content": "对产品成分没有研究，辣个有名买辣个，果然，不适合我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969580}, {"id": 178441, "content": "专业办理各种教师资格证，幼师证，幼儿园园长证、学历提升、网络教育、成人高考、医师证，建筑八大员，电工证，焊工证，建造师，特殊机械操作证等等。\n疯狂报名中，办证需要时间，为了确保每一位的证件没有失误，提前提交资料预约，联系方式：zcy13653200379(同微信)无意者请勿扰\n", "image": "img/option/option/20170314100527hm7sli8nLaC9ASwZ", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968908}, {"id": 178442, "content": "好多皮肤好的说自己什么也不涂，我不涂就完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272133}, {"id": 178443, "content": "美容院的坑，保养品的懵，水面膜的扔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 178444, "content": "花了不少冤枉钱，到最后发现只要做好保湿和防晒，皮肤自然一切都好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969621}, {"id": 180237, "content": "祛痘路上很坎坷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973482}, {"id": 178190, "content": "认为天生丽质", "image": null, "praise_count": 219, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916550}, {"id": 178446, "content": "敏感皮还学别人去角质", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750408}, {"id": 179470, "content": "花了很多钱祛痘，然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299712}, {"id": 178447, "content": "我 熬夜（围笑） ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969666}, {"id": 178192, "content": "乱买买买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957506}, {"id": 178449, "content": "抽烟喝酒熬大夜却妄图用化妆品补救", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825069}, {"id": 178194, "content": "到现在都没搞清楚自己算是什么肤质，只好凭直觉买个大概", "image": null, "praise_count": 439, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 178453, "content": "过度清洁是永远的痛。还有一定要听皮肤科医生的话。不然激素脸啊啊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681075}, {"id": 178454, "content": "丑爆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903152}, {"id": 178455, "content": "法国美国小众医学品牌尝试一遍，发现还是钟爱SKII。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139718}, {"id": 178456, "content": "有痘痘，医生说不让擦任何护肤品，可是脸好油，要是不油的话不就要补水？又不能用护肤品，好纠结啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969809}, {"id": 179736, "content": "不洗脸的时候就安慰自己脸油可以保养皮肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964942}, {"id": 178202, "content": "敏感皮跟风用上了洗脸皂……结果冬天干的脸泛红，大家慎重啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440054}, {"id": 178460, "content": "好多闲置 还买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938344}, {"id": 180253, "content": "喜新厌旧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973692}, {"id": 178206, "content": "弯路就是买了很多不适应的东西，最后学会看成分看产地，推荐一个查成分的网站CosDna", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968526}, {"id": 178463, "content": "折腾了它?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933493}, {"id": 178210, "content": "出门老是忘记涂防晒", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878462}, {"id": 178213, "content": "误认为自己大油皮瞎用护肤品", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 178216, "content": "看见别人用啥就买啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821061}, {"id": 183080, "content": "去角质，大学以为一天一次。还好后来因为懒没继续用了。现在皮肤没以前好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 40203}, {"id": 178217, "content": "总是相信那些“神奇”的祛痘产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931774}, {"id": 178219, "content": "青春期脸上没有痘，但是学别人用曼秀雷敦，就真的想了痘，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913058}, {"id": 178222, "content": "一直在拿脸做实践的路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849064}, {"id": 178478, "content": "挤黑头留坑了怎么办?只能攒钱去做光子嫩肤了，护肤美容就是一条有去无回的路啊，永远在路上?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898540}, {"id": 178223, "content": "洗完脸忘了用水和乳，直接上隔离开始化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653221}, {"id": 178224, "content": "跟风", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960410}, {"id": 178480, "content": "油痘皮千万少折腾\n油痘皮千万少折腾\n油痘皮千万少折腾\n重要的是说三遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946364}, {"id": 178226, "content": "防晒霜太白，不肯抹，透明的呢，又特么觉得这玩意有用吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 178227, "content": "我到底是什么肤质？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 178228, "content": "不知道自己啥时候看起来帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936298}, {"id": 178229, "content": "其他不说，把油性皮肤变成超级敏感肌了", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892328}, {"id": 178485, "content": "重庆妹纸除了夏天总觉得其他三个季节晒不到太阳，每天都在纠结防晒霜到底搽不搽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942061}, {"id": 178230, "content": "用到现在真马油最好", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965914}, {"id": 178231, "content": "把自己折腾成了敏感肌(´°̥̥̥̥̥̥̥̥ω°̥̥̥̥̥̥̥̥｀)\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968092}, {"id": 186935, "content": "挤痘痘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991320}, {"id": 178232, "content": "每次买到适合自己的护肤品也只能适合一段时间，没多久就又要换了", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968513}, {"id": 178233, "content": "初三起，痘就没消过，愁", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958066}]}